<h2>Confirm Your Email Address</h2>

<p>Hello <strong><%= @user.email %></strong>,</p>

<p>Thank you for registering with <strong>ParañaqueConnect</strong>, Parañaque City's official community reporting system!</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1e40af;">Email Confirmation Required</h3>
  <p>To complete your registration and start using ParañaqueConnect, please confirm your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
</div>

<div style="text-align: center;">
  <%= link_to 'Confirm My Email', confirmation_url(@user, confirmation_token: @confirmation_token), class: 'button' %>
</div>

<div class="info-box">
  <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1e40af;">Your Account Details</h3>
  <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @user.email %></p>
  <p><strong>Role:</strong> <%= @user.role.titleize %></p>
  <p><strong>Account Created:</strong> <%= @user.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %></p>
</div>

<h3>What You Can Do (After Confirmation):</h3>
<ul>
  <% if @user.resident? %>
    <li><strong>Report Issues:</strong> Submit reports about problems in your community</li>
    <li><strong>Add Photos:</strong> Upload photos to help describe the issue</li>
    <li><strong>Pin Location:</strong> Use our map to pinpoint exact locations</li>
    <li><strong>Add Comments:</strong> Communicate with barangay officials</li>
    <li><strong>Track Progress:</strong> Monitor the status of your reports</li>
  <% elsif @user.barangay_official? %>
    <li><strong>Manage Reports:</strong> View and respond to reports from your barangay</li>
    <li><strong>Update Status:</strong> Change report status (pending, in progress, resolved)</li>
    <li><strong>Respond:</strong> Add comments and communicate with residents</li>
    <li><strong>Dashboard:</strong> Monitor barangay activity and statistics</li>
  <% elsif @user.admin? %>
    <li><strong>System Management:</strong> Manage categories, barangays, and users</li>
    <li><strong>System Overview:</strong> Monitor all reports and system activity</li>
    <li><strong>User Management:</strong> Create and manage user accounts</li>
    <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> View system-wide statistics and reports</li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<div style="background-color: #fef3c7; padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; margin: 30px 0;">
  <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #92400e;">Important</h4>
  <p style="margin: 0;">This confirmation link will expire in 24 hours. If you didn't create an account with ParañaqueConnect, please ignore this email.</p>
</div>

<div style="background-color: #dbeafe; padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; margin: 30px 0;">
  <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1e40af;">Getting Started Tips</h4>
  <ul style="margin: 0;">
    <li><strong>Complete your profile</strong> after confirming your email</li>
    <li><strong>Explore the dashboard</strong> to see available features</li>
    <li><strong>Read the guidelines</strong> for submitting effective reports</li>
    <li><strong>Contact support</strong> if you need any assistance</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div style="background-color: #f0f9ff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9; margin: 30px 0;">
  <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #0c4a6e;">Need Help?</h4>
  <p style="margin: 0;">If you have any questions or need assistance:</p>
  <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">
    <a href="mailto:paranaqueconnect@deidei.tech">paranaqueconnect@deidei.tech</a><br>
    Phone: (02) 8820-7300<br>
    Website: <a href="<%= root_url %>">ParañaqueConnect</a>
  </p>
</div>

<p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">
  <strong>Thank you for joining ParañaqueConnect!</strong><br>
  Together, we can make Parañaque City a better place for everyone.
</p>
